name: UBC SISA Sauder First Year Conference
description:
Are you an incoming Sauder student?
Have questions regarding courses and professors?
Want tips on how to excel in COMM 101 or COMM 290?
Worried that virtual classes will make it harder for you to make new friends in university?
We’ve all been there (except it wasn’t online :D), so Sauder International Student Association (SISA) wants to help you as much as we can! Check out our event Sauder 101 and all of your questions and worries will be answered!

**Location:** Vibevent - SISA will be partnering with this platform to bring out this amazing event for you - more details to follow.
**Time:** July 15th, 2020, 9 PM PST

We are so excited to welcome you to Sauder - SISA is here so do not fear!
